ata.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/KSDV/111%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c1084%2c20221116%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"KSDV,111,訴,1084,20221116,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"1084","JDATE":"20221116","JTITLE":"侵權行為損害賠償"}